            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Alphabet公司(A)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>)截至台北時間30日22:56股價上漲21.33美元，報371.27美元，漲幅6.1%，成交量26,111,567（股），盤中最高價377.03美元、最低價365.82美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+1.14%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.43%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.03%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.84%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Alphabet公司(A)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+3.13%</li> <li>近 1 月：+27.56%</li> <li>近 3 月：+3.46%</li> <li>近 6 月：+27.45%</li> <li>今年以來：+11.8%</li></ul></section></main>",
